:{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584425541011","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1,1],"flex":"row","padding":10},"children":[{"type":"panel","id":1584427474423,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[0.61,1.3900000000000001],"flex":"column","padding":10,"fontSize":40},"children":[{"id":"text21584425541011","value":"沉闷的课件","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":false}},{"type":"image","id":1584427501228,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/t4AiCKolTcs6Pyw.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":"$1584427780470","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584427477478,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[0.63,1.37],"flex":"column","padding":10,"fontSize":40},"children":[{"id":1584427483940,"value":"无聊的报表","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":false}},{"type":"image","id":1584427508578,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/bncwEAaoZ4SQT5y.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":"$1584427780470","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584425599930,"value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1.2,1],"flex":"row","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584425599930","value":"想要解决","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$2","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"right","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":1584702840926,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[0.92,1.08],"flex":"column","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text21584425599930","value":"现在制作幻灯片的软件存在一些一言难尽的问题.....","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"bottom","padding":50,"isTitle":false},"_children":null},{"type":"image","id":1584702854466,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/K2zf6tVYerh5Gp8.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584425744663,"value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1.38,0.6200000000000001],"flex":"row","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584425744663","value":"未来的工作","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$2","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"right","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"id":"text21584425744663","value":"因为这最初只是一门课的课设，时间紧张，不论是是代码实现上还是功能上都还不优雅。\n\n但现在成了我的毕设，所以还有很多工作需要完成。","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":50,"isTitle":false}}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584426239062,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584426239062","value":"有一些零散的想法","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584426239062","value":"column","attrs":{"span":[0.81903975,1.06381025],"flex":"column","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text21584426239062","value":"最开始也许你只有一些零散的想法，完全不知到底要讲啥。这时你需要的就是把所有的想法收集起来。\n\n这个阶段你可以将想法（文字、图片...)添加到想法面板，最后再将它们直接拖拽进幻灯片。","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false},"_children":null},{"type":"image","id":1584436200521,"value":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/20/829AAK.png","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":27,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584426274509,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584426274509","value":"想法变成了大纲","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584426274509","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[0.8054669999999999,1.2598329999999998],"flex":"row","padding":0},"children":[{"id":"text21584426274509","value":"随着想法收集的越来越多，你要讲述的内容的大纲就愈发清晰。\n\n这时你就可以在大纲面板进行大纲的构建，大纲里面每一个观点都会对应创建一页幻灯片。\n\n同时你可以随时通过拖拽对大纲进行修改。","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false},"_children":null},{"type":"image","id":1584704437385,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/DUSlW1YQ5hxRZps.png","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584426364804,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584426364804","value":"设计每一页幻灯片","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584426364804","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[0.9951,0.8648999999999999],"flex":"row","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text21584426364804","value":"在大纲构建完成后就可以开始设计每一页幻灯片了。\n\n传统的软件因为幻灯片中元素间没有任何关系，所以需要大量的拖拽和对齐操作进行布局，是一个无聊且费时的操作。\n\n在结构面板将视觉元素（文字、图片）通过一棵树组织起来，对这棵进行的拖拽操作会直接影响每一页幻灯片的展示形式。","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false},"_children":null},{"type":"image","id":1584437073506,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/sAoUkqYWXZ9Bwvu.png","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":0,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584426390597,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584426390597","value":"调整结构和样式","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584426390597","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[0.6762,0.9338000000000001],"flex":"row","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text21584426390597","value":"现在到了调整结构和样式的时候了，对于拥有相同属性的元素单独调整样式不得不说很麻烦。比如如果希望调整所有的字体颜色为红色，只有一张张幻灯片的调整。\n\n可以在属性面板创建属性变量，然后直接拖拽进对应的属性和它关联起来。当修改该变量的时候，相关联的属性都会发生变化。","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false},"_children":null},{"type":"image","id":1584439891664,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/Aei1nRBtIVhg2p9.png","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":0,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584426576731,"value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1.35,1.4],"flex":"row","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"type":"panel","id":1584708304151,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[0.5125,0.7375],"flex":"column","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text1584426576731","value":"存在的问题","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":120,"color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true},"_children":null},{"id":"text21584426576731","value":"现在还有很多问题：当前的幻灯片布局还是不太方便、不支持动画、图形化设计能力太弱、大纲上每一个观点对应一页幻灯片有所限制、使用起来有学习成本......\n\n当然 Bug 应该也是不少的....","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false},"_children":null}],"_children":null},{"type":"image","id":1584708027112,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/20/XZl3GcEU5ohR6vp.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"},"_children":null}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584426591329,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584426591329","value":"需要帮助","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584426591329","value":"column","attrs":{"span":[0.7819999999999999,1.0579999999999998],"flex":"column","padding":10,"fontSize":35},"children":[{"id":"text21584426591329","value":"当然上面的很多问题目前都有了解决方案，不过还是需要大家的帮助。\n大家使用 uIdea 时候遇见的问题和 bug 都可以给我提出。\n同时在制作幻灯中遇见的问题或者是想要的功能，都可以联系我。","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false}},{"type":"image","id":1584508042920,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/1hCrUjy5JbaG78x.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584427592805,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584427592805","value":"而是用来","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"bottom","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584427592805","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1,1,1],"flex":"row","padding":10},"children":[{"type":"image","id":1584427985363,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/19/98BpPJuXqfCEiLl.png","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}},{"id":"text21584427592805","value":"当你有一些有意思、炫酷的东西或者故事想和大家分享","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","padding":50,"isTitle":false}},{"type":"image","id":1584427975787,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/LzxSiW9AywPtVOE.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center","fontSize":80}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584428658202,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584428658202","value":"词云模式","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584428658202","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1.13,0.8700000000000001],"flex":"row","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text21584428658202","value":"一般的幻灯片制作软件只有两个模式：编辑模式和放映模式，但是在这里拥有一种第一无二的模式：词云模式。\n\n让用户一眼看出你有啥有趣的想法，而其中哪些又是最重要的。\n\n点击“放映”按钮进入放映模式，按下“esc”键即可进入词云模式，uIdea 会自动对每一页幻灯片进行布局！！！","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false}},{"type":"image","id":1584446163660,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/dpaqzgCYJ9I2UnW.png","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584428694143,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584428694143","value":"听众走神","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$3","color":"$5","fontWeight":"bold","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"center","padding":0,"isTitle":true}},{"type":"panel","id":"panel1584428694143","value":"row","attrs":{"span":[1,1],"flex":"row","padding":10},"children":[{"id":"text21584428694143","value":"在播放幻灯片时候听众走神是在正常不过的事了。\n\n这除了和你的演讲技巧和内容有关，还和你幻灯片的切换动画有关。\n\n但传统软件幻灯片之间的切换，不仅不能引起听众足够的重视，而且也无法让他们知道前后两张幻灯片的关系。自然而然就走神了......","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSize":"$4","color":"$5","fontWeight":"normal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","padding":0,"isTitle":false}},{"type":"image","id":1584504981263,"value":"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/18/oRylUJxBGgfvYmt.jpg","attrs":{"displayMode":"normal","padding":10,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"center"}}]}]},{"type":"panel","id":1584428696433,"value":"column","attrs":{"span":[1,2],"flex":"column","padding":"$1584502387986","backgroundColor":"$1"},"children":[{"id":"text1584428696433","value":"Point 不 Power","type":"text","attrs":{"fontSi